<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .code-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìß Verify Your Email</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello!</h2>

            <p>Thank you for signing up for Finder App! To complete your registration, please verify your email address.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= link %>" class="button">
                    Verify Email Address
                </a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</strong></p>
            <p
                style="background: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px;">
                <%= link %>
            </p>

            <div
                style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This verification link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>If you didn't create an account with Finder App, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Finder Team</p>
            <p>This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you have any questions, contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>